    },
    {
      "content": "？？？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:59"
    },
    {
      "content": " 祸不单行？",
      "intimacy_delta": 0.01,
      "role": "User",
      "timestamp": "10:59"
    },
    {
      "content": "你还记得经常在大饭店门口讨饭的那个流浪汉吗？",
